{"tid":414370,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚悉尼既巴絲打...請入!","createTime":"2017-09-26T07:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T03:45:02.000Z","uid":73311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08e16d58c2599209d22fae7e0354a097075b34b7","tid":414370,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"有冇人係悉尼好悶想一齊出黎玩下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左黎悉尼出trip 3個星期<br />\n我計過仲有好多日無野做....<br />\n想約下巴絲打出黎食飯/飲野/行街/去景點<br />\n但求有人陪下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我已經去左:<br />\nBlue Mountain National Park<br />\nBondi Beach<br />\nNew Town<br />\nSydney Opera House<br />\nDarling Harbour<br />\nFish Market<br />\nCircular Quay<br />\nThe Rocks<br />\n<br />\n未去因為無車<br />\nHunter Valley<br />\nPart Stephens<br />\n<br />\n打算去<br />\nArt Gallery of NSW<br />\nTaronga Zoo<br />\nNewcastle<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有好推薦? <br />\n岩玩可以一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我可以陪下你都得...<br />\n但求唔好悶死係悉尼姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食下野 吹下水都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd58115862264527c71bb9e8f6fd9dfc36f251a","tid":414370,"uid":73311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"悉尼有冇咩冷門景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d809ae703655c03f9d10f9a696e35561cb650069","tid":414370,"uid":79823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"去manly beach <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nJervis Bay 都值得去 （沿路可以去埋wollongong同kiama 但要2日一夜）"},{"pid":"ef05b3516e88ecb8d405afda31208beb45e9e9ac","tid":414370,"uid":73311,"like":0,